# Rasm Bash Scripts

**Required**: `coding-bash` skill (`~/.codex/skills/coding-bash/SKILL.md`).

## Script roles (do not conflate)

| Script | Rail |
|--------|------|
| `scripts/check-cs.sh` | Static: build, format, analyzer — no tests |
| `scripts/test.sh` | `dotnet test` unit specs |
| `scripts/rhino.sh` | Rhino bridge: build, doctor, check, verify, package, deploy |

## Conventions

- Bash 5.2+/5.3, `set -euo pipefail` (or repo-established strict prelude)
- Dispatch-table routing over nested conditionals
- Atomic I/O, signal-safe cleanup
- Validate with `bash -n` and `shellcheck` before completion

## Bridge script changes

Run the validation ladder in `tools/rhino-bridge/AGENTS.md` serially; bridge and static gates share build caches and one live Rhino endpoint.
